    "In fact, a deviation is introduced by the Wiener filter, and certain high-order terms are neglected when constructing the template.",
    "Therefore, we express B temp S as:B temp S = B lens + N ′,(2.25)where N ′ denotes the bias induced by both the Wiener filter and the method itself.",
